---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
    title="Day Zero Solutions - Operations software for hospitality and aged care"
    description="Day Zero is an Australian software studio. NutriCare for aged care dietary safety and RestroAI for restaurant operations: deep, live products with a domain-grounded AI agent at the core."
    canonical="https://day-zero.com.au/"
    ogTitle="Day Zero Solutions - Operations software for hospitality and aged care"
    ogDescription="An Australian software studio building NutriCare for aged care and RestroAI for restaurants, with a domain-grounded AI agent at the core."
    isHome={true}
>
    <!-- ========== HERO ========== -->
    <section class="hero" id="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <p class="hero-tag">From Day Zero to Day One.</p>
            <h1 class="hero-title">Building the solutions<br><span class="gradient-text">that get you ready</span><br>for Day One.</h1>
            <p class="hero-sub">We build software for <span id="typewriter" class="typewriter-word">hospitality</span>. Real tools for the real operation, from the kitchen pass to the care floor.</p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
                <a href="#products" class="btn btn-primary">See the products</a>
                <a href="#book-demo" class="btn btn-outline">Book a demo</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-glow"></div>
        <div class="hero-glow-2"></div>
        <div class="hero-glow-3"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- ========== THESIS ========== -->
    <section class="thesis" id="thesis">
        <div class="container">
            <p class="section-tag">Why we exist</p>
            <h2 class="thesis-title">Same regulation. Same operator pain.<br>A different cheque size.</h2>
            <div class="thesis-body">
                <p>Hospitality and aged care are demanding, tightly regulated, low-margin businesses. The people who run them deserve software built around how the work actually happens: the resident's dietary profile, the IDDSI texture level, the supplier invoice, the compliance record. Not generic tools they have to bend their operation around.</p>
                <p>The regulation is the same whether you run one site or fifty. The operator pain is the same. The cheque is not. Day Zero builds software that fits the operator, the regulation, and the budget at the same time.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ========== FLAGSHIP PRODUCTS ========== -->
    <section class="products" id="products">
        <div class="container">
            <p class="section-tag">Flagship products</p>
            <h2 class="section-title">Two products, live and deep.</h2>
            <p class="section-sub">Each built end to end for its industry, in production today, and run by real operators.</p>

            <!-- NutriCare -->
            <div class="product-card product-nutricare">
                <div class="product-info">
                    <span class="product-kicker"><i class="fas fa-heart-pulse"></i> Aged care</span>
                    <h3 class="product-name">NutriCare</h3>
                    <p class="product-tagline">The dietary safety and care-intelligence platform for aged care.</p>
                    <p class="product-desc">From resident dietary profiles to the kitchen tray and back. Real-time allergen and IDDSI texture conflict detection, malnutrition screening, and the compliance evidence the strengthened Aged Care Quality Standards now demand, daily.</p>
                    <ul class="product-features">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Allergen &amp; IDDSI texture conflict detection at the point of order</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> MUST screening, weight trends, intake tracking, SIRS-ready incident logs</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Clinical evidence to ESPEN 2022, GLIM 2019, AND/ASPEN, Quality Standard 6</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> NutriAssist AI, family portal, FHIR R4 export, 10-role RBAC, full audit trail</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="product-pricing"><i class="fas fa-tag"></i> From <strong>A$10 per resident / month</strong>, 30-day free trial, volume discounts for larger facilities. Pilot deployments available.</p>
                    <div class="product-cta-row">
                        <a href="https://www.nutri-care.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-primary">Visit nutri-care.app</a>
                        <a href="#book-demo" class="btn btn-outline">Book a demo</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="product-visual">
                    <div class="app-mockup mockup-nutricare">
                        <div class="mockup-chrome">
                            <div class="mockup-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
                            <span class="mockup-url">nutri-care.app</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mockup-body">
                            <div class="mockup-resident-card">
                                <div class="mockup-avatar"></div>
                                <div class="mockup-resident-info">
                                    <div class="mockup-res-name">Margaret Wilson</div>
                                    <div class="mockup-badges">
                                        <span class="mbadge mbadge-iddsi">IDDSI 4: Pureed</span>
                                        <span class="mbadge mbadge-allergen">Gluten Free</span>
                                        <span class="mbadge mbadge-allergen">Dairy Free</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mockup-stats-row">
                                <div class="mockup-mini-stat"><span>24</span><small>Residents</small></div>
                                <div class="mockup-mini-stat"><span>3</span><small>Pending</small></div>
                                <div class="mockup-mini-stat accent"><span>100%</span><small>Compliant</small></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mockup-meal-row">
                                <span class="mockup-meal done">Breakfast ✓</span>
                                <span class="mockup-meal done">Lunch ✓</span>
                                <span class="mockup-meal pending">Dinner -</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- RestroAI -->
            <div class="product-card product-restrostock">
                <div class="product-info">
                    <span class="product-kicker product-kicker-mint"><i class="fas fa-utensils"></i> Restaurants</span>
                    <h3 class="product-name">RestroAI</h3>
                    <p class="product-tagline">The operating system for independent Australian restaurants.</p>
                    <p class="product-desc">The back office and the floor in one system. Procurement with 3-way matching, recipe costing and menu engineering, online ordering, kitchen display, and HACCP, tuned to Australian suppliers, GST, and food-cost realities.</p>
                    <ul class="product-features">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Inventory, purchase orders, goods receipts, invoice OCR &amp; 3-way matching</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Recipe costing &amp; menu engineering (stars / dogs), waste analytics</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Online ordering, QR menus, kitchen display, reservations, loyalty</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Predictive ordering, smart procurement &amp; RestroAI chat on the data</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="product-pricing"><i class="fas fa-tag"></i> Plans from <strong>A$49/month</strong> (or A$490/year), 15-day free trial, no credit card required.</p>
                    <div class="product-cta-row">
                        <a href="https://restroai.app" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn-mint">Explore restroai.app</a>
                        <a href="#book-demo" class="btn btn-outline">Book a demo</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="product-visual">
                    <div class="app-mockup mockup-restrostock">
                        <div class="mockup-chrome">
                            <div class="mockup-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
                            <span class="mockup-url">restroai.app</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mockup-body">
                            <div class="mockup-stat-cards">
                                <div class="mockup-stat-card sc-green"><span>$12.4k</span><small>Stock Value</small></div>
                                <div class="mockup-stat-card sc-amber"><span>4</span><small>Low Stock</small></div>
                                <div class="mockup-stat-card sc-blue"><span>8</span><small>Open POs</small></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mockup-chart">
                                <div class="mockup-bar" style="--h: 60%"></div>
                                <div class="mockup-bar" style="--h: 80%"></div>
                                <div class="mockup-bar" style="--h: 45%"></div>
                                <div class="mockup-bar" style="--h: 90%"></div>
                                <div class="mockup-bar" style="--h: 65%"></div>
                                <div class="mockup-bar" style="--h: 75%"></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="mockup-alert-strip">
                                <i class="fas fa-triangle-exclamation"></i> Tomatoes: 2 kg, reorder now
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ========== AGENTIC AI SIGNATURE ========== -->
    <section class="agent-sig" id="ai">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="agent-head">
                <p class="section-tag">How our AI works</p>
                <h2 class="section-title">AI that answers to the record.</h2>
                <p class="agent-lead">Most software bolts a chatbot on the side. Ours reads the live operational record, reasons over it, and shows its working. The same agent pattern runs across our products: no invented data, no guesses on a resident's safety or a night's food cost.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="agent-cards">
                <!-- NutriAssist (NutriCare) -->
                <div class="agent-card" aria-hidden="true">
                    <div class="agent-card-head">
                        <span class="agent-card-dot"></span> NutriAssist
                        <span class="agent-card-tag">NutriCare</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="agent-msg agent-msg-user">
                        Can Robert Chen have the grilled salmon for dinner?
                    </div>
                    <div class="agent-msg agent-msg-bot">
                        <p><strong>No.</strong> Two conflicts on Robert's profile:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><span class="agent-flag flag-red">Allergen</span> Grilled salmon uses a gluten-based marinade. Robert has a documented <strong>gluten allergy</strong>.</li>
                            <li><span class="agent-flag flag-amber">Texture</span> The dish is served IDDSI Level 7 (Regular). Robert is prescribed <strong>Level 4 (Pureed)</strong>.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="agent-cite">Source: Robert Chen, dietary profile, updated 2 days ago.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- RestroAI chat -->
                <div class="agent-card" aria-hidden="true">
                    <div class="agent-card-head agent-card-head-mint">
                        <span class="agent-card-dot agent-card-dot-mint"></span> RestroAI chat
                        <span class="agent-card-tag agent-card-tag-mint">RestroAI</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="agent-msg agent-msg-user agent-msg-user-mint">
                        Why is my food cost up this week?
                    </div>
                    <div class="agent-msg agent-msg-bot">
                        <p><strong>Up 2.3 points to 34.1%.</strong> The main driver is chicken breast:</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li><span class="agent-flag flag-amber">Price drift</span> Sunrise Poultry billed <strong>$9.80/kg</strong>, 14% above the 90-day average of $8.60.</li>
                            <li><span class="agent-flag flag-blue">Impact</span> About <strong>$130</strong> extra at this week's usage. Two suppliers quote under $8.90.</li>
                        </ul>
                        <p class="agent-cite">Source: invoice INV-2043, Sunrise Poultry, received 2 days ago.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <ul class="agent-points">
                <li><i class="fas fa-database"></i> <strong>Grounded.</strong> Every answer is retrieved from your own records in real time, scoped to your site.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-list-check"></i> <strong>Verifiable.</strong> It cites the profile, the texture level, the invoice line. You can check the working.</li>
                <li><i class="fas fa-scale-balanced"></i> <strong>Regulation-aware.</strong> It speaks IDDSI, allergens, HACCP, and food cost, not generic prompts.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ========== QUEUEZERO (EMERGING) ========== -->
    <section class="emerging" id="coming-soon">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="emerging-card">
                <div class="emerging-info">
                    <span class="product-kicker product-kicker-orange"><i class="fas fa-bolt"></i> In development</span>
                    <h3 class="emerging-name">QueueZero</h3>
                    <p class="emerging-desc">Mobile ordering and queue-busting for food trucks and pop-ups. Customers order ahead, you cook ahead. No app to download, no hardware to buy. In active development, with a foundation cohort forming now.</p>
                    <form class="waitlist-form" id="waitlistForm">
                        <div class="waitlist-input-group">
                            <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email" required>
                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-orange">Join the waitlist</button>
                        </div>
                        <p class="waitlist-hint">Foundation cohort gets locked-in launch pricing. No spam.</p>
                    </form>
                </div>
                <div class="emerging-visual">
                    <div class="product-icon-wrap icon-orange">
                        <i class="fas fa-bolt"></i>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ========== COMPLIANCE BAND ========== -->
    <section class="compliance" id="compliance">
        <div class="container">
            <p class="section-tag">Built for Australian regulation</p>
            <h2 class="section-title">The standards are in the product, not the brochure.</h2>
            <div class="compliance-chips">
                <span class="compliance-chip">IDDSI</span>
                <span class="compliance-chip">Aged Care Quality Standards</span>
                <span class="compliance-chip">SIRS</span>
                <span class="compliance-chip">HACCP</span>
                <span class="compliance-chip">FHIR R4</span>
                <span class="compliance-chip">Privacy Act 1988</span>
                <span class="compliance-chip">GST / ABN / BAS</span>
                <span class="compliance-chip">ESPEN 2022</span>
                <span class="compliance-chip">AU data residency</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ========== BOOK A DEMO ========== -->
    <section class="book-demo" id="book-demo">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="demo-grid">
                <div class="demo-info">
                    <p class="section-tag">See the product</p>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Book a 15-minute demo</h2>
                    <p class="demo-desc">Tell us which product you'd like to see and when works for you. We'll send a calendar invite within one business day.</p>
                    <ul class="demo-benefits">
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> See the product live, not a recording</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Ask questions specific to your facility or restaurant</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> No sales pressure. A genuine look at the product.</li>
                        <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> 15 minutes, done</li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="demo-stats">
                        <div>
                            <span class="demo-stat-num">15 min</span>
                            <span class="demo-stat-label">Demo length</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="demo-stat-num">&lt; 24 hrs</span>
                            <span class="demo-stat-label">Response time</span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <span class="demo-stat-num">Free</span>
                            <span class="demo-stat-label">No commitment</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <form class="demo-form" id="demoBookingForm">
                    <div class="demo-form-row">
                        <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your name" required>
                        <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Email address" required>
                    </div>
                    <input type="text" name="organisation" placeholder="Facility / restaurant name">
                    <select name="product" required>
                        <option value="" disabled selected>Which product?</option>
                        <option value="nutricare">NutriCare (aged care dietary management)</option>
                        <option value="restroai">RestroAI (restaurant operations)</option>
                        <option value="queuezero">QueueZero (mobile ordering, early access)</option>
                        <option value="multiple">Multiple products</option>
                    </select>
                    <div class="demo-form-row">
                        <select name="preferred_day">
                            <option value="" disabled selected>Preferred day</option>
                            <option>Monday</option>
                            <option>Tuesday</option>
                            <option>Wednesday</option>
                            <option>Thursday</option>
                            <option>Friday</option>
                            <option>Any day</option>
                        </select>
                        <select name="preferred_time">
                            <option value="" disabled selected>Preferred time (AEST)</option>
                            <option>Morning (9am to 12pm)</option>
                            <option>Lunchtime (12pm to 2pm)</option>
                            <option>Afternoon (2pm to 5pm)</option>
                            <option>Any time</option>
                        </select>
                    </div>
                    <textarea name="message" placeholder="Anything specific you'd like to see in the demo? (optional)" rows="3"></textarea>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary btn-full">
                        <i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i> &nbsp;Request a demo time
                    </button>
                    <p class="demo-disclaimer">We respond within one business day. No spam, ever.</p>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ========== CONTACT ========== -->
    <section class="contact" id="contact">
        <div class="container">
            <p class="section-tag">Say hello</p>
            <h2 class="section-title">Let's build something together.</h2>
            <p class="section-sub">Want to see a product? Use the booking form above. For anything else, here's how to reach us.</p>
            <div class="contact-methods contact-methods-row">
                <a href="mailto:hello@day-zero.com.au" class="contact-item">
                    <div class="contact-icon"><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i></div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Email us</strong>
                        <p>hello@day-zero.com.au</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
                <a href="#book-demo" class="contact-item">
                    <div class="contact-icon"><i class="fas fa-calendar-check"></i></div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Book a demo</strong>
                        <p>15 minutes, no commitment</p>
                    </div>
                </a>
                <div class="contact-item">
                    <div class="contact-icon"><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i></div>
                    <div>
                        <strong>Based in</strong>
                        <p>Brisbane, Australia</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script>
        import '../scripts/home.js';
    </script>
</Base>
